  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Welcome to the Stream</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>And You're Tonight's Star</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Just when you're about to watch your favorite streamer, you realize something is off.  The house he is looking at, <i>it's yours</i>, and he just broke in.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Run, hide until the cops come, find a way to escape your house, without running away on foot, for his \"accomplices\" hides in the bushes. Check the stream to find out where the Streamer is at, read chat while in a closet, if that's what you're into.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Several mid game events to spice up the survival.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3 Endings to achieve.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Controls: </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Left Click: Open/Close Doors; Hide in closets and curtained bathtubs; Interact</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Right Click: Watch the stream</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shift: Sprint</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ctrl (or C): Crouch</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >E: Pick Up/Pickpocket Items</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >F: Flashlight</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >X/Y: <i>Lean</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3203420/extras/6f2430d0e9b96800b8acda9f38bb2874.poster.avif?t=1744481761\" width=250 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3203420/extras/6f2430d0e9b96800b8acda9f38bb2874.webm?t=1744481761\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3203420/extras/6f2430d0e9b96800b8acda9f38bb2874.mp4?t=1744481761\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Additional information about what's in the game:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It is a one map game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A killer to avoid.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A puzzle to solve.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Plenty of items to pick up.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Plenty of hiding spots.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There is an internal timer in game.</p>",
